name: EMPIRE x Money Man Big Money Album Release Party

metadata.name: EMPIRE x Money Man Big Money Album Release Party
metadata.description: Empire x Money Man Big Money commemorative NFT. This NFT gives you exclusive access to Money Man's Big Money album release party on June 24th, 2022. This coin serves as access to the event and the opportunity to meet and greet with Big Money himself. Once you have purchased please visit https://nft.empi.re/bigmoney for instructions on how to access your QR Code.
